TEXAS REAL ESTATE EXECUTIVES, THE DANIELS GROUP - GILMER

data.description: Welcome Home! This beautiful home is located on a serene street in the outskirts of Gilmer. Situated in a fantastic neighborhood and boasting a prime location, this property offers the perfect blend of tranquility and convenience.  Featuring 3 spacious bedrooms and three full bathrooms, this home spans across an impressive 2,440 square feet. The floor plan provides ample space for comfortable living.  One of the highlights of this property is the backyard, that has shade from the beautiful trees and the two storage/workshops, both equipped with electricity. These versatile spaces provide endless possibilities for hobbis, crafts, or additional storage needs. The two car garage has its own storage on the backside with its own garage door to the back yard, perfect for your lawn equipment.  To sweeten the deal, the seller is offering a $7,000 credit towards flooring with an acceptable offer. This allows you the opportunity to customize the home to your liking, Make it truly your own.
